descriptionHTML:
Super Royal Jump will bring back all your childhood memories through this classic platform version of the game. The thrill of jumping and running with your brothers & sisters.. dash through the worlds and steal all the acorn gold you love. Desa Adventure you never would have seen, the old school play merged with new arcade elements jabb-ing through the pixels. Let us take you back to your childhood in this completely ads free game!

Finn's gold acorns were stolen by an evil monster and taken to his childhood world. To get his pine gold back, Finn's King orders him to enter the leprechaun world and beat the monster. Collect gold, acorns, and lots of free fun!

Super Royal Jump Features
- Over 80+ challenging levels, more levels are coming soon
- Super Stunning graphics, run & jump better
- Different monsters' worlds have different skills
- Boost your fun with the awesome jumps
- Steal a large amount of pine gold!

Enjoy! the amazing free zuper adventures of King Velha and Finn through the leprechaun world!
